Whenever you want, sir
- How about tonight?

57
00:08:19,818 --> 00:08:21,615
Hey Karan, Good evening,
come on in

58
00:08:22,888 --> 00:08:23,946
Good evening sir
- Hi

59
00:08:24,756 --> 00:08:26,018
Meet Capt. Manjit Dhingra

60
00:08:26,458 --> 00:08:27,982
Hello, nice to meet you
- Nice to meet you

61
00:08:28,226 --> 00:08:29,693
Lt. Vishal Srivatsav

62
00:08:30,562 --> 00:08:31,620
and Capt. Ramanna

63
00:08:32,964 --> 00:08:37,958
My God! Did you guys see that?
Ramanna actually smiled!

64
