How cold does it get
up there in winter, sir?

212
00:20:01,686 --> 00:20:04,154
Minus forty degree, minus fifty degree
- Really

213
00:20:04,355 --> 00:20:07,153
Yes, it's difficult to stay up there

214
00:20:08,025 --> 00:20:11,825
Both, the pakistanis and
we vacate our posts in winter

215
00:20:12,363 --> 00:20:14,331
It's like a gentleman's pact

216
00:20:14,866 --> 00:20:17,835
that neither of us will
take advantage of this

217
00:20:18,536 --> 00:20:21,994
Once the weather changes,
we man our posts again

218
00:20:23,875 --> 00:20:25,001
I'd like to go there, sir

219
00:20:27,378 --> 00:20:28,675
Someday you'll have to

220
00:20:35,887 --> 00:20:36,854
Check
- Check

221
00:20:37,555 --> 00:20:40,023
Sure you aren't a cousin of our
Grandmaster vishwanath Anand?!

222
00:20:41,225 --> 00:20:43,193
Good morning sir
- Hey morning

223
00:20:43,728 --> 00:20:44,194
Coffee?

224
00:20:44,896 --> 00:20:45,521
Why not?

225
00:20:46,230 --> 00:20:48,027
Ashok, another cup please?
- Yes, sir

226
00:20:54,472 --> 00:20:54,938
from home

227
00:20:57,074 --> 00:20:59,542
Do you like mangoes?
- Sir?

228
00:20:59,744 --> 00:21:00,369
Mangoes?

229
00:21:02,079 --> 00:21:02,704
I like them

230
00:21:04,582 --> 00:21:05,879
Ever eaten mangoes from Maliyabad?

231
00:21:06,584 --> 00:21:08,882
I will if you get them, sir

232
00:21:10,087 --> 00:21:12,055
The fun lies in eating
them fresh at the orchard

233
00:21:13,090 --> 00:21:13,715
Hey, Mishra!

234
00:21:15,092 --> 00:21:16,559
Want to come home and eat
mangoes next season?

235
00:21:16,928 --> 00:21:19,055
You plan this every year
but never take me there!

236
00:21:19,764 --> 00:21:21,732
I wonder if he really has
any orchards at all!

237
00:21:22,934 --> 00:21:23,901
Come on! It's your move

238
00:21:25,269 --> 00:21:26,736
Check!
- Again?!

239
00:21:30,942 --> 00:21:31,408
Why don't you...

240
00:21:39,450 --> 00:21:40,075
Hey Karan...

241
00:21:41,285 --> 00:21:43,082
Isn't she the girl whose
picture is in your wallet?

242
00:21:47,625 --> 00:21:50,423
What happened? A tiff?

243
00:21:54,632 --> 00:21:55,257
Excuse me sir

244
00:22:38,676 --> 00:22:40,644
Hey Rajiv
- Hi brother

245
00:22:40,845 --> 00:22:41,641
What's up?

246
00:22:42,013 --> 00:22:42,638
Where you coming from?

247
00:22:44,181 --> 00:22:44,806
There

248
00:22:51,856 --> 00:22:52,652
Where's Romi?

249
00:22:53,190 --> 00:22:56,648
She's busy preparing
for tomorrow's protest march

250
00:22:57,695 --> 00:22:59,663
protest match? Again!?

251
00:23:05,703 --> 00:23:08,501
Okay friends, the pamphlets are here

252
00:23:08,706 --> 00:23:13,006
Now our volunteers must be at
every gate by 7 in the morning

253
00:23:13,210 --> 00:23:14,677
Okay?
- We'll be there

254
00:23:15,546 --> 00:23:17,514
Every student should
be given one, Okay?

255
00:23:17,715 --> 00:23:19,182
And please ask them to read it

256
00:23:19,383 --> 00:23:21,010
pamphlets are meant to be read

257
00:23:22,887 --> 00:23:24,184
Is this poster okay?

258
00:23:24,889 --> 00:23:25,355
Good

259
00:23:26,057 --> 00:23:28,025
Where are the Hindi posters?

260
00:23:28,225 --> 00:23:30,022
Almost complete Don't worry

261
00:23:30,561 --> 00:23:34,520
Okay I'm going home
Call me if you need anything

262
00:23:34,732 --> 00:23:36,359
Or tomorrow at 7 A. M, okay?

263
00:23:36,567 --> 00:23:37,033
Hi Karan

264
00:23:38,736 --> 00:23:39,202
What's going on?

265
00:23:39,403 --> 00:23:41,371
Preparation for the march

266
00:23:41,572 --> 00:23:46,032
put up posters opposite
the vice Chancellor's office...

267
00:23:46,243 --> 00:23:47,369
...this very night, okay?

268
00:23:47,578 --> 00:23:49,876
No more of the vice
